  <%- include('includes/header')%>

    <main>
        <section class="section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">Our Story</h2>
                <div class="content-wrapper">
                    <div class="text-content">
                        <h3>Empowering Creativity, One Frame at a Time.</h3>
                        <p>LensLeap was born from a simple idea shared among passionate student filmmakers and photographers: professional equipment shouldn't be a barrier to creativity. We noticed how often amazing projects were limited by access to high-quality gear.</p>
                        <p>Our mission is to provide fellow students and aspiring creators with affordable, accessible, and reliable camera equipment. We meticulously maintain our inventory and offer friendly support to ensure you have the right tools to bring your vision to life. Whether it's a short film, a photoshoot, or a personal project, we're here to support your creative journey.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="image-content">
                        <img src="/uploads/about.jpg" alt="Image of about"/>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    
